                            et l'excellence.</span>
                        </h2>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- section end-->
        <div class="row offset-margin">
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-4">
                <div class="categorie-item"><img class="img--bg" src="{{asset('/images/focusbook.jpg')}}" alt="img" />
                    <div class="categorie-item__details"><span class="categorie-item__pretitle"><span
                                class="color--orange">
                            </span></span>
                        <h4 class="categorie-item__title"><span class="color--orange">I</span><span class="color--white">nvesti</span>
                        </h4>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-4">
                <div class="categorie-item"><img class="img--bg" src="{{asset('/images/youcando.jpg')}}" alt="img" />
                    <div class="categorie-item__details"><span class="categorie-item__pretitle"><span
                                class="color--orange"></span></span>
                        <h4 class="categorie-item__title"><span class="color--orange">P</span><span class="color--white">assionné</span>
                        </h4>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-4">
                <div class="categorie-item"><img class="img--bg" src="{{asset('/images/diplomehat.jpg')}} " alt="img" />
                    <div class="categorie-item__details"><span class="categorie-item__pretitle"><span
                                class="color--orange"></span></span>
                        <h4 class="categorie-item__title"><span class="color--orange">D</span><span class="color--white">iplômée</span></span>
                        </h4>
                    </div>
                </div>
    </section>
